name: Nike Sportswear Bucket Hat
description: A classic, essential bucket hat from the Nike Sportswear collection in a clean, solid white. This unisex hat is crafted from soft yet durable 100% cotton twill, making it lightweight and comfortable for all-day wear. It features a 360-degree brim that provides ample sun protection, perfect for summer days or outdoor activities. The front is adorned with a woven Nike Futura logo patch, adding a signature, sporty touch to the minimalist design. This hat is a versatile accessory for both casual and athletic styles.

name: Nike Sportswear Core Kids' Bucket Hat
description: A classic Nike Sportswear bucket hat, scaled down for kids. This essential hat comes in a versatile solid black and is crafted from soft yet durable 100% cotton twill for lightweight comfort. Its 360-degree brim provides excellent sun protection, making it perfect for outdoor play, family outings, and sunny days. The front features a clean, woven Nike Futura logo patch in white, adding a signature touch to this timeless and functional accessory for both boys and girls.

name: Nike Sportswear Heritage 86 Metal Swoosh Cap
description: A timeless and versatile unisex cap from the Nike Sportswear Heritage 86 collection. This classic 6-panel hat is presented in a clean white and is crafted from lightweight, 100% recycled polyester fabric featuring Dri-FIT technology to help wick away sweat. The design is distinguished by a sleek, metallic Swoosh logo ingot on the front panel for a premium, elevated look. It features a pre-curved brim and an adjustable strapback closure with a metal buckle, ensuring a personalized and comfortable fit for everyday wear.

name: Puma Scuderia Ferrari Race Cap
description: A classic 6-panel baseball cap from the Puma Motorsport collection, celebrating the racing heritage of Scuderia Ferrari. This unisex hat comes in a clean white and is crafted with recycled materials. The front features a bold red stripe and the iconic Scuderia Ferrari shield as a premium silicone badge. The design includes a pre-curved brim with red trim and an adjustable snapback closure for a comfortable, customizable fit. An embroidered Puma Cat logo on the back completes this essential accessory for motorsport fans.

name: The North Face Recycled 66 Classic Cap
description: An eco-conscious and timeless baseball cap, The North Face Recycled 66 Classic. This hat is crafted entirely from 100% recycled polyester in a deep navy blue, offering a sustainable choice without sacrificing style. It features a classic 6-panel design with a pre-curved brim. The front is adorned with a tonal, embroidered The North Face logo for a subtle and sophisticated look. An adjustable strapback closure ensures a comfortable and customizable fit, making it the perfect versatile accessory for daily wear, hiking, and any outdoor adventure.

name: adidas Terrex 5-Panel Trail Running Cap
description: An ultralight and highly breathable 5-panel cap from the adidas Terrex collection, engineered for trail running and outdoor adventures. This unisex hat is crafted from 100% recycled polyester in a light grey color. It features extensive laser-cut perforations on the side panels for maximum ventilation, designed to keep you cool on the move. The lightweight fabric also offers UPF sun protection. The front panel displays the adidas Terrex logo, and an adjustable webbing strap at the back ensures a secure, personalized fit. This is a high-performance cap for hitting the trails or navigating the city.

name: Nike Sportswear Apex Washed Bucket Hat
description: A stylish unisex bucket hat from the Nike Sportswear Apex collection, perfect for adding a touch of color and vintage flair to any outfit. This hat is crafted from a soft yet durable 100% cotton gabardine fabric and features a washed treatment for a comfortable, lived-in feel. Its mid-depth design and 360-degree brim provide ample coverage and a classic look. The front is adorned with the iconic Nike Futura logo, embroidered in a contrasting white, showcasing signature brand style.

name: Nike Sportswear Club Unstructured Camo Cap
description: Complete your everyday look with the Nike Sportswear Club Cap, featuring a timeless woodland camouflage print. This unisex hat is crafted from soft and breathable 100% cotton twill. It has an unstructured, 6-panel 'dad hat' design with a pre-curved brim for a comfortable, relaxed feel from the first wear. The front features the iconic Nike Futura logo embroidered in a tonal black, blending seamlessly with the camo pattern. An adjustable strapback closure at the back ensures a perfect, customizable fit.

name: Puma Scuderia Ferrari Race Cap
description: A classic 6-panel baseball cap from the Puma Motorsport collection, celebrating the racing legacy of Scuderia Ferrari in a bold black and yellow colorway. This unisex hat is crafted with recycled materials, reflecting a commitment to sustainability. The front features a vibrant yellow stripe and the iconic Scuderia Ferrari shield as a premium silicone badge. The design includes a pre-curved brim with contrasting yellow trim and an adjustable snapback closure for a comfortable, customizable fit. This cap is the perfect accessory for motorsport enthusiasts and fans of Formula 1.

name: Nike Sportswear Tech Fleece Fly Cap
description: A modern, low-profile 5-panel cap from the Nike Sportswear collection, crafted from Nike's iconic Tech Fleece fabric. This unisex Fly cap comes in a versatile heather grey and is made from a soft, lightweight, and warm cotton-polyester blend. The unstructured design provides a comfortable, relaxed feel. It features a dark bonded tape accent across the front for a technical look, and a Nike Futura logo is printed on the side. An adjustable webbing strap with a buckle at the back ensures a secure and personalized fit.
